1. cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper deals with image analysis and uses computer vision techniques to estimate body shapes and clothing categories from images. 
2. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper involves the analysis of multimedia data (images) to understand clothing preferences based on body shape. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses machine learning techniques to build a predictive model for clothing categories given body shape. 
4. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction): The paper has implications for human-computer interaction, as it could be used to develop personalized clothing recommendations based on body shape. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper involves the retrieval of information from online sources (images) to understand clothing preferences based on body shape.
